{"pedagogical-reasoning":"I should affirm the student's direction while pushing them to use evidence and specificity. I will avoid confirming a final answer and instead give a simple verification standard. Then I will ask a question that leads them to classify BU based on evidence, keeping it concise and Socratic.","Student-facing-answer":"Not too random if you can support it. Don’t guess—verify.

Use this standard: include an actor only if you found some sign they research, advise, partner, advocate, fund, or implement climate-related work in Boston.

So for BU, what evidence do you have: research only, partnership with city efforts, or direct role in action?"}
